nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Negative Prompt)
widgets_values: 色调艳丽，过曝，静态，细节模糊不清，字幕，风格，作品，画作，画面，静止，整体发灰，最差质量，低质量，JPEG压缩残留，丑陋的，残缺的，多余的手指，画得不好的手部，画得不好的脸部，畸形的，毁容的，形态畸形的肢体，手指融合，静止不动的画面，杂乱的背景，三条腿，背景人很多，倒着走

ref_image = subject
control_video = pose control
ref_motion = camera motion (basically)
The control_video and ref_motion need to match up decently well, can get weird results if they don't. Also, for large camera movement, control_video length should match audio length

widgets_values: A realistic human with windy hair talking with a lot of expression. looking straight, looking in the camera. The Person is excited and  talks extremely passionately. Dynamic background Effects
